    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard and that the quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96, all QoI differences < 10%) provide sufficient confidence to accept the model for the stated COU. The overall credibility evidence supports regulatory submission.",
